|---------|---------|---------|--------------|
| three | 0.160.0 | 3D rendering | The standard for web 3D |
| @react-three/fiber | 8.15.0 | React renderer for Three.js | Declarative 3D, better DX |
| @react-three/drei | 9.92.0 | Helpers and abstractions | Solves common problems |
