- Copied toast: Check icon turns green for 2s
- Shiki themes: github-light / github-dark (auto-detect from document class)
- Default supported languages: typescript, javascript, python, css, html, json, bash, shell, sql, yaml, markdown, xml, rust, go, java, cpp, c, ruby, php, swift, kotlin
</action>

